<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>CCC Merch – Cricket CrowdCast</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="hero">
    <h1>Cricket CrowdCast Shop</h1>
    <p>Rep the commentary culture with CCC fashion and collectibles!</p>
  </header>

  <main class="shop">
    <section class="product">
      <img src="/images/ccc-baggy-hat.png" alt="CCC Baggy Cream Hat" width="200">
      <h3>CCC Baggy Cream Hat</h3>
      <p>The iconic crowdcap. Limited stock!</p>
      <button>Add to Cart - $25</button>
    </section>

    <section class="product">
      <img src="/images/ccc-shirt.png" alt="CCC Shirt" width="200">
      <h3>CCC Shirt</h3>
      <p>Chirp like a legend in this cotton beauty.</p>
      <button>Add to Cart - $20</button>
    </section>

    <section class="product">
      <img src="/images/ccc-ball.png" alt="Signed Cricket Ball" width="200">
      <h3>Signed Cricket Ball</h3>
      <p>Official merch signed by mystery crowd legend “Screamer Sid.”</p>
      <button>Add to Cart - $40</button>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
